item.title: You Won't Believe What Happens Next: How You Like That
item.description: IV Conclusion Introduction In June 2020, the K-pop girl group BLACKPINK released their single “How You Like That,” which quickly became a global sensation From its catchy chorus to its powerful music video, the song quickly gained millions of views and streams, becoming one of the most popular songs of the year In this essay, we’ll explore the impact of “How You Like That” on both the group and the culture at large
